Package: PivotRedcapTable
Title: Transform REDCap Pseudo-Tables into Analyzable Format
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Diana", "Rinker", , "dianarinker@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reshapes REDCap checkbox and repeating instrument exports from wide 
    pseudo-table format into tidy long-format data frames ready for analysis. 
    Designed for clinical research workflows using REDCap at academic medical centers.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    purrr,
    stringr,
    haven,
    here 
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
